Xtento_AdvancedOrderStatus

-------------
  CHANGELOG
-------------

===== 1.0.0 =====
 * Initial release

===== 1.0.1 =====
 * Bugfix release

===== 1.0.2 =====
 * Bugfix release

===== 1.0.3 =====
 * Fixed a bug that could lead to wrong "Notified" / "Not Notified" states in the order status history

===== 1.0.4 =====
 * Prevented duplicate emails from being sent

===== 1.0.5 =====
 * Adjusted adminhtml controller to cope with full page caches better

===== 1.0.6 =====
 * Notification emails are sent regardless if Magentos order comment emails are enabled or not

===== 1.0.7 =====
 * Fixed a bug where only one notification would be sent for many orders during bulk processing

===== 1.0.8 =====
 + Added resource reset script for failed DB installations/updates

===== 1.0.9 =====
 * Fixed a bug that could cause order update emails to be sent out twice, for the old and new status, when adding comments from the Sales > Orders view in the Magento backend

===== 1.0.10 =====
 + Added further possible controller_names to the Observer to match more grids

===== 1.1.0 =====
 + Added ability to hide/show only specific order statuses in the "Status" dropdown when changing the order status
 ! Confirmed compatibility with Magento CE 1.9.0.0 / EE 1.14.0.0

===== 1.1.1 =====
 * Various bugfixes and code optimization in license code

===== 1.1.2 =====
 * Fixed a bug in Xtento_AdvancedOrderStatus_Model_Sales_Order_Status_History -> "Fatal error: Call to a member function save() on a non-object..."